snippet.title: Hacknet Labyrinths
snippet.description:
COMING SOON ON STEAM: http://store.steampowered.com/app/521840/

Join a small team of elite hackers pulling off a complex series of data heists in Hacknet Labyrinths, a major expansion for critically acclaimed terminal-based hacking simulator, Hacknet.

Trailer music by Rémi Gallego: http://soundcloud.com/remigallego - in association with The Otherworld Agency: http://theotherworldagency.bandcamp.com

FOLLOW HACKNET
WEB: http://hacknet-os.com
TWITTER: @hacknetOS
